== About ==
Pixel Quest! is an Open world 2D perma-death MMORPG focusing on Bullet Hell combat with Roguelike elements. The game focuses on leveling your character and completing quests through defeating enemies and bosses, collecting better loot and searching for rare legendary drops! There are over 30+ dungeons, 200+ unique legendaries, 80+ bosses, 150+ unique skins. Although dying results in character loss, you are awarded with valor which you can use to become stronger, purchase items, and progress!
